lead_paragraph: South Africa coach Russell Domingo hopes his side’s comprehensive 280-run victory in the fourth test against England will halt the criticism levelled at the side after successive series defeats knocked them off the top of the world rankings.

headline.print_headline: South Africa Coach Domingo Hopes Win Will Quieten the Noise
